[INFO ] 2026-07-20 10:20:42.057 [jdbc.sqlonly.sqlOccurred(31)]  - SQL:

        SELECT combo.*
         , COALESCE((SELECT LANG_DESC
                     FROM DOCS_LANG
                     WHERE LANG_CD = combo.LANG_CD
                       AND LANG_TYPE = 'ko'), combo.TEXT) AS LANG_DESC
    FROM DOCS_COMBO combo
